metadata.name: Last Period
metadata.description:
Global climate change affects all living species.  The waters receded.All the fishes died.And the last remaining puddle of water is about to dry.  Migratory birds are on their way.  Black storks have to feed and go http://on.Black storks don't like to eat dead fish. This stork's only hope is a few live fish in the pond. Maybe the stork was with its shadow for the last time.
